text: Ahmed Abou El Fotouh (; born 22 March 1998), sometimes referred to by his nickname Fattouh (), is an Egyptian footballer who plays for Egyptian Premier League side Smouha, on loan from Zamalek, and the Egyptian national team as a defender. ==Honours== ===Club=== ;Zamalek *Egypt Cup: 2017–18 ===Egypt=== *Africa U-23 Cup of Nations Champions: 2019 ==References== Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Egyptian footballers Category:Egypt youth international footballers Category:Egypt international footballers Category:Association football defenders Category:Egyptian Premier League players Category:Zamalek SC players Category:ENPPI SC players Category:Smouha SC players
